---
title: Mini Chicken Caesar Wraps with Spiced Potato Rounds
description: All the flavours of a classic chicken Caesar, but in quick, fuss-free handhelds! Crisp spinach and tomato are the base for creamy, cheesy dressing and steak-spiced baked chicken.
